{"tid":1794901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港警甴出左2019年6月至10月犯罪比率","createTime":"2019-12-23T13:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T13:33:51.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a53b01a739514870ebcbd4a61027bb559e7eef37","tid":1794901,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"官方數據網址： <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/csd.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F09_statistics%2Fcsd.html&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4bc3b84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/csd.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月：3808<br />\n2019年7月：4333<br />\n2019年8月：4466<br />\n2019年9月：4825<br />\n2019年10月：6437<br />\n<br />\n除左十月外，基本上香港犯罪率冇咩點上升<br />\n<br />\n此外，2019年6月至8月的犯罪率，比2018年同期還要低。<br />\n<br />\n直至2019年9月才略高於2018年9月。"},{"pid":"23a0cc21de563639a52865a8ba1735c5757269e3","tid":1794901,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"原來真係沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n咁勁的示威活動，又咁勇武，咁多「暴徒」，又火燒港鐵和警署。<br />\n<br />\n每星期都有「暴力」示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n香港治安都無明顯惡化。<br />\n<br />\n香港人質素真係高。"},{"pid":"9c8815024106141dedba14e81c9407af949df017","tid":1794901,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"條數扣埋班義士分分鐘無變過"},{"pid":"64a20c233603257010cd421486495173f32ddf6a","tid":1794901,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c8815024106141dedba14e81c9407af949df017","tid":1794901,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"條數扣埋班義士分分鐘無變過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0285eed581c4c928810be5043e9d8c0358c1bf51","tid":1794901,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c8815024106141ded